    - Centralized Information: All project data, communications, and metrics in one place.
    - Real-Time Collaboration: Instant updates enhance teamwork and accountability.
    - Customizable Layout: Tailor your dashboard to show only relevant metrics.
    - Integration Flexibility: Connect with over 1,000 business and project management tools.
